node.text:
Top of the top guys. Started the day wit a Repost from the coldest 🥶 The OG Chazz Palminteri speaking Big Facts 🎯
@icet #IceColdFacts .....
I can post a thousand quotes to support this.... "With no struggle there's no progress."- Frederick Douglass 
"To live is to suffer... to survive is to find meaning in the suffering."-DMX
"Don't focus on the pain,focus on the progress."- The Rock
"I dont run from pain, I run to it and get through it."-Tip
Pick one and progress.
